Weekly Specials at Banko Cantina & Other Events
Taco Tuesday All You Can Eat Tacos for 18.99 Music by DJ Blandz • Rooftop opens at 6PM. $3 Tacos – Chicken, Steak, and Beef.  $4 Fish or Shrimp.
$5 Lobster.  $4 Mexican Beers, $25 Select Margarita Pitchers & More!  Happy Hour 5-8PM.
Thursday Happy Hour 5-8PM Bar and Tables, $7 Martinis 5pm – 11pm
Roof Top Opens 7pm with Complimentary Drink For Ladies 9pm – 10:30PM (Roof Top Only) Calladita Thursday on the roof top 9pm – 3am
Friday Roof Top opens at 6PM. Second Floor opens at 10 PM. Live Music By Mojito Latin Band on the 1st Floor 9 PM Restaurant opens at 5 PM.  Ask you server about our Bottle Specials.  Ladies Drink Free from 8 PM-10 PM on the Rooftop. DJs and Music on All Floors. Party til 4 AM.
Saturday Ask about our $250 Bottle Package & other specials! Mojito Latin Band on the 1st Floor 10PM. DJs on our 2nd Floor and Rooftop. Happy Hour continues from 5PM-8PM.
Party til 4 AM on all Three Floors.
Sunday Roof Top Opens 1pm $20 Bottomless Mimosas with Food Purchase. $25 Bottomless Mimosas without a Food Purchase.
Brunch 11 AM to 3 PM with full Brunch Menu. After Party 2PM. DJs on Roof Top

Legendary Holiday Decor
Christmas Pop Up Bar
You won't be disappointed in our #SantaBankoBaby Christmas Bar Menu filled with Santa's Snacks and Ice Cold Cocktails.  Enjoy Merry Manhattan's and Classic Holiday Sliders to really add to the amazing ambience we have created unlike no other.  We offer Hot Chocolate, Cinnamon Rolls, and Festive Cocktails that will even make the Grinch Happy every Holiday Season.
Santa Banko Baby
"Young, hip vibe with fabulously fresh take on traditional Mexican cuisine. Finishing off the meal with a beautiful plate of churros.  Decorated for Christmas to the max!  Lovin' it!  But honestly ,the food was the star. Don't miss this place."
Shelby - North Carolina

Let Banko create a Memorable Event
Banko Cantina is located within the Heart of Downtown West Palm Beach.  With Three different Floors to choose from, your next event will be one for the Books.  Contact us today!
Book Now
We're Here To Help You Plan Your Event
For a Direct Email with Immediate Attention, please contact lenny@BankoCantina.com who is in charge of our Private Events and include details for your request.  Or fill out the Contact information below.  We look forward to working with you.
Restaurant
Our dining room is Spacious and offers an Intimate Setting.  Whether you're celebrating a Birthday, Bachelorette Party or Office Mixer, Banko Cantina is the Perfect choice for your next Event.
